rU2h","ref":"Exod.35.6","text":"And blue, and purple, and scarlet, and fine linen, and goats’ hair,","year":-1491},{"id":"recmw93tEvvilsVFn","ref":"Exod.35.7","text":"And rams’ skins dyed red, and badgers’ skins, and shittim wood,","year":-1491},{"id":"recPqtSyT5YXvIomc","ref":"Exod.35.8","text":"And oil for the light, and spices for anointing oil, and for the sweet incense,","year":-1491}]}
